12-27T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"一定要呢隻狗坐監"},{"pid":"0adc4526c50c3f4152ba9772c67a17bb86c9f25e","tid":1799793,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"《立場新聞》記者日前被警員截查時，有警員於直播鏡頭前展示身分證。警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓表示，警員當時手持記者的身分證，被記者的攝錄機拍下，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警員做法有不對，警方會主動調查，並配合私隱專員公署的工作。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n郭嘉銓說，涉事警員<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">未有停職，會繼續執勤</span></strong>，指警方重視個人私隱，一直要求警員按照相關指引及守則行事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCLS 連認錯都唔敢, 做錯左又敢講......&quot;不對&quot; 咪即係錯哂囉~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca1e5c398b8cf7234b67d8cb7bfaade71bacbea","tid":1799793,"uid":338097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:56:33.000Z","msg":"昇哥好野"},{"pid":"20a6dc98e2944b821d7fe481d2bb3da9a80256d9","tid":1799793,"uid":325884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:10:13.000Z","msg":"告鳩佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最高刑罰坐5年及罰100萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16d16c57ece6e4c57029e13d6042065059343c8","tid":1799793,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:20:44.000Z","msg":"大家幫手宣傳下，ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同你身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sa5sWmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSa5sWmr.jpg&h=2e6a418c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2skMss7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2skMss7.jpg&h=077c238a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門<br />\n<br />\n德國聯署要人！倒數四日！但得一萬人咋！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1798520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1798520</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最新日程表出咗啦 除夕元旦都有行動呀<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/1798785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1798785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}